sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Platform Ingress
    participant RestProxy as rest-proxy Sidecar<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Marshaler as CustomJSONPb<br/>Marshaler
    participant GRPCClient as gRPC Client<br/>(GRPCInferenceService)
    participant GRPCSrv as gRPC Inference Server<br/>localhost:8033/TCP

    Note over Client,GRPCSrv: Flow 1: REST Inference Request

    Client->>RestProxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>TLS optional
    RestProxy->>Marshaler: Unmarshal JSON request body
    Note right of Marshaler: Parse tensor data types<br/>(BOOL, INT8-64, UINT8-64,<br/>FP32/64, BYTES)<br/>Handle base64 binary content
    Marshaler->>GRPCClient: ModelInferRequest (protobuf)
    GRPCClient->>GRPCSrv: gRPC ModelInfer RPC<br/>TLS optional<br/>Max msg: 16 MiB (configurable)
    GRPCSrv-->>GRPCClient: ModelInferResponse (protobuf)
    GRPCClient-->>Marshaler: Response protobuf
    Note right of Marshaler: Marshal tensor outputs<br/>to JSON arrays
    Marshaler-->>RestProxy: JSON response body
    RestProxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 OK<br/>Content-Type: application/json

    Note over Client,GRPCSrv: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request

    Client->>RestProxy: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>TLS optional
    RestProxy->>GRPCClient: ModelMetadataRequest (protobuf)
    GRPCClient->>GRPCSrv: gRPC ModelMetadata RPC<br/>TLS optional
    GRPCSrv-->>GRPCClient: ModelMetadataResponse (protobuf)
    GRPCClient-->>RestProxy: JSON response
    RestProxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 OK<br/>Model metadata JSON
